1. *Ostaje* nam da čekamo odgovor. (We are left to wait for the answer.) 
2. Ona *ostaje* naša jedina nada. (She remains our only hope.)
3. Ono što je *ostalo* nije značajno. (What has been left is not significant.)
4. *Ostati* ćeš bez posla ako ne počneš da radiš više. (You will remain jobless if you don't start working harder.)
5. Oni su već *ostali* bez novca. (They have already run out of money.)